    "body": "@laanwj: If we take a closer look at a `AmountFromValue`, than i think, `CAmount` can be `0` so `AmountFromValue()` should also be able to handle `0`ness. Even, a single function must not/should not represent the behavior of the whole system (if someone would define our system behavior to reject 0 values everywhere).\n`AmountFromValue` is also used in `createrawtransaction` and there i could imaging usecases for 0 value in/outputs (to replace later by some hex/further manipulating, etc.).\n\n**Therefore ACK this solution (even if it's a slightly API change).**\nAnd yes, adding a test for a 0 value would probably be a good idea.\n",
